  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/11/28/google-play-store-now-highlights-chromecast-friendly-apps/\"><img alt=\"Chromecast section in Google Play\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/a5bf4e543766e599633c4e3f97b32af3/google-play-chromecast-section.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n继新增了「<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/22/google-play-tablet-device-optimized/\">专为平板而设</a>」的应用分区后，Google Play 今天又为那些供 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/chromecast\">Chromecast</a> 电视棒使用的软件安置了「新家」。从现在开始，用户在通过 Android 设备浏览 Google Play 时将可以看到 Chromecast 分区，其中除了 Google 自己的媒体应用外，还有 HBO Go、Hulu Plus、Netflix、Pandora 等服务。暂时来看应用的数量还不算多，但未来其规模应该会越来越大吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/27/google-play-store-now-highlights-chromecast-friendly-apps/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://9to5google.com/2013/11/27/google-adds-chromecast-specific-app-section-to-play-store-app/\" target=\"_blank\">9to5 Google</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/28/google-play-store-now-highlights-chromecast-friendly-apps/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20777883/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/28/google-play-store-now-highlights-chromecast-friendly-apps/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
